.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
City: hannover, miami, marseilles, nizza, hamburg
There are 5 different nationalities: english, spanish, ukranian, norwegian, japanese
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-gold, kools, chesterfields, lucky-strike, parliaments
The people have 5 different hobbies: rock-climbing, gardening, writing, drawing, sudoku
5 different pets are kept: dog, fox, zebra, horse, snails

1. the english is the person traveling to hannover
2. the spanish is the owner of the dog
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person traveling to miami
4. the ukranian is the person who's hobby is gardening
5. the person traveling to miami is to the right of the person traveling to marseilles
6. the old-gold-smoker is the owner of the snails
7. the kools-smoker is the person traveling to nizza
8. the person who's hobby is writing is in the middle
9. the norwegian is on the far left
10. the chesterfields-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the fox
11. the kools-smoker is to the left or right of the owner of the horse
12. the lucky-strike-smoker is the person who's hobby is drawing
13. the japanese is the parliaments-smoker
14. the norwegian is to the left or right of the person traveling to hamburg

.:: Answer ::.
